---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
List or inspect background jobs (large batch mutations, progress, undo ids).

Job history is persisted locally and survives a daemon restart; the most recent jobs are retained.

Usage: mxr jobs [OPTIONS] [JOB_ID]

Arguments:
  [JOB_ID]
          Optional job id to inspect. Omit to list recent jobs

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>
          [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
